Class DataDay

  • java.lang.Object
    • StatisticsAbstract
      • DataDay

  • public class DataDay
extends StatisticsAbstract
    Version:
    10/05/2016
    Author:
    CS2334. Modified by: Kyle Roller, Nigel Mansell

    Date: 10/25/2016
    Project 3

    This class represents a summary of one day's data from a single Mesonet station.
